FBIS4-8281 "dreeu070__a94049" FBIS-EEU-94-070-A Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 ANNEX Hungary AWACS Planes Flew Solely Under UN Mandate AWACS Planes Flew Solely Under UN Mandate AU1104200994 Budapest MTI in English 1553 GMT 11 Apr 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU1104200994 Budapest MTI English BFN [Text] Budapest, 11 April 11 (MTI) -- AWACS surveillance planes flew patrols in Hungarian airspace both on Sunday [10 April] and Monday, Defense Ministry spokesman Lieut.- Col. Lajos Erdelyi told MTI today, stressing they flew solely under a UN Security Council mandate. The spokesman declined to answer whether or not the monitoring aircraft had been in Hungary's airspace during NATO air attacks on Bosnian Serb military positions around Gorazde.
